Milestone 0.6:
--------------
* New command: print. Print a variable to stdout.
* Isolated mode: run zenfig only taking default variables and facts (including defaults from the kit being used)
  Flag parameter name: --only-defaults -x
* Change output_file key to dest in index schema
* A more practical user variable directory: move it from ~/.local/share to ~/.zenfig
* log messages as filters: log_msg, log_msg_warn, log_msg_err. This will allow templates to log output.

Milestone 0.7:
--------------
* Proper kit schema marshalling
